## 5. Duplicate Dashboard Overview Pages

`/dashboard/agent/marketing/page.tsx` and `/dashboard/agent/marketing/management/page.tsx` **render identical layouts** using the same hook (`useCommandCenter`) and the same four components (`CurrentTaskKpi`, `DashboardStatsRow`, `DashboardTaskList`, `ReadOnlySchedule`). The only difference is a `<h1>` title and a `Surface` wrapper on the error state.

> [!WARNING]
> One of these pages is redundant. The sidebar links "Command Center" → `/management` and "Overview" → the marketing root. Both show the same command-centre data. If the data model of these two pages is supposed to differ in the future, there is no current separation of concern to build on.

